summary:
A civil and structural engineer with 8+ years of experience in infrastructure projects in Sri Lanka, Netherlands and Norway.  Always looking for new challenges and opportunities to serve in an adaptive environment. At present, working in the oil and gas industry in Norway. 

•	Experience in the design of reinforced concrete and steel structures to Euro Codes & British Standards 
•	Wide knowledge of StaadPro, Prokon, SAP2000 and AutoCAD software packages
•	Chartered civil and structural design engineer (IESL, Sri Lanka)
